<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Free 2025 Gaming Giveaways & Skin Codes</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f1a;
      color: #e0e0ff;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 60px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6e48aa 0%, #00d2ff 100%);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: white;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto 40px;
      color: #f0f0ff;
    }

    .form-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 0 auto 60px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }
    .form-box input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 12px 0;
      border: 1px solid #444;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .form-box input::placeholder { color: #aaa; }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      background: #ff3366;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 18px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 20px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #ff1a57; transform: translateY(-3px); }

    .trust {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #a0a0ff;
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    footer a { color: #00d2ff; text-decoration: none; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      header h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; }
      header { padding: 60px 15px 40px; }
      .form-box { padding: 40px 25px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Get Free Skin Codes & Giveaways 2025</h1>
      <p>Weekly updated list of working free skins, items, beta keys & epic giveaways — sent straight to your inbox. Join 18,000+ gamers already claiming rewards!</p>

      <div class="form-box">
        <form action="https://your-email-service.com/submit" method="post">
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your best email..." required>
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Gamer tag / name (optional)">
          <button type="submit" class="btn">GET MY FREE LIST NOW →</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="trust">✓ No spam • Unsubscribe anytime • 100% free</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <footer>
    <p>Privacy Policy • We respect your inbox • © 2025 YourBrand</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>